                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><Icon name="archive" class="icon" title="Scheduled backups" /></div>
                    <h4>Scheduled backups</h4>
                    <p>Add files/folders to a scheduled Gmail backup list from Finder, then manage timing/labels in the app.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><Icon name="text" class="icon" title="Text actions" /></div>
                    <h4>AI actions for selected text</h4>
                    <p>Select text in any app and run AI actions: analyze, translate, look up definitions, summarize, explain, and grammar check.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><Icon name="bubble" class="icon" title="AI Chats" /></div>
                    <h4>AI Chats</h4>
                    <p>Use the app for ongoing conversations with files, follow-ups, and local history. Export conversations when needed.</p>
